<plot>Filmed in the country where dancehall began, this film incorporates the best of the local Jamaican dancehall selectors, DJ's and dancers. Together in one "Dance-U-Mentary", all the key figures of dancehall describe the style, history, and language of the culture. IT'S ALL ABOUT DANCING shows the essence of dancehall through candid interviews inter-spliced with dance sequences that can teach anyone the basics of this phenomenon.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?270137</url></doc>
